Human data pool for AI training exhausted in 2024 ' Elon Musk
Published by
Tribune
on Fri, 10 Jan 2025
Tribune OnlineHuman data pool for AI training exhausted in 2024 ' Elon MuskTesla CEO Elon Musk has stated that all available human data for Artificial intelligence (AI) training, including books, was exhausted in 2024. This assertion aligns with conclusions reached by other experts in the field. During a livestream conversation with Mark Penn, chairman of Stagwell, Musk made these comments, which were streamed on X.
